article_title: Aetna CEO's Cure For Obamacare Requires Congressional Remedy

article_metadata.description: Aetna CEO Mark Bertolini said changes needed to fix problems with public exchanges will need an act of Congress and that's not going to happen anytime soon.
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
